    "problemStatement": "Given an integer array nums, return all unique triplets [nums[i], nums[j], nums[k]] such that:\n\ni \u2260 j, i \u2260 k, j \u2260 k\n\nnums[i] + nums[j] + nums[k] = 0\n\nThe solution set must not contain duplicate triplets.",
